      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "人聞きの悪いことを言わないでくれ\n俺はストーカーなんてしたことはないぞ",
      "startTime": 209.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01-aoi021.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、ごめんごめん\n君はストーカーじゃなくて覗き魔だったね",
      "startTime": 214.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01-aoi022.m4a",
      "text": "怜から話は聞いてるよ、君につきまとわれて\n覗き魔されたのがデビューのきっかけだって",
      "startTime": 222.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
